In 6.0.1 pipes are working. But I need to use another method for PSSessionOption:

$PSSessionOptionOverride = New-Object System.Management.Automation.Remoting.PSSessionOption -Property  @{'MaximumReceivedObjectSize'=5242880;'Culture'='en-US';'NoMachineProfile'=true;'CancelTimeout'=150000000;'OperationTimeout'=450000000;'IdleTimeout'=600000000;'OpenTimeout'=150000000;ProxyAccessType=0}

For some reason I need to write 600000000 to receive 60 seconds IdleTimeout. It looks like new bug in powershell client 6.0.1.
